    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s honestly in flawless, showroom-ready shape and looks like it just rolled off the lot! It drives like a dream and has been my total pride and joy. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and is ready to hit the road without a single worry, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin, you're going to love it! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
