      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this beauty. This car has been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s basically in showroom condition! I\u2019ve babied it since day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, regularly detailed, and honestly still has that fresh new-car feel. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here; it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
