      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that provides seamless variable valve timing. The high-revving valvetrain is meticulously calibrated, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is reached with linear power delivery. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a fully documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings and dampers to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Every surface, from the Laguna Seca Blue finish to the Nappa leather bolsters, is preserved in a showroom-correct state, free of oxidative wear or mechanical fatigue.",
